{"tid":1481522,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"原來大陸狗想來搗亂香港，跟住嫁禍香港人，便可出動解放軍！","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T17:57:18.000Z","uid":170601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0dd57be573e8996f78ccf2c2b8936d81d49c975","tid":1481522,"uid":170601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:46:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E6%8E%89%E5%87%BA-%E7%AE%B1%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF3%E7%94%B7-130248668.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%25A7%2581%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BB%258A%25E6%258E%2589%25E5%2587%25BA-%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF3%25E7%2594%25B7-130248668.html&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1CwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=864e74ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91%E7%A7%81%E5%AE%B6%E8%BB%8A%E6%8E%89%E5%87%BA-%E7%AE%B1%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF3%E7%94%B7-130248668.html</a>"},{"pid":"2e390b1e5a0ac2f757dfe6b344612f66ef5d31ea","tid":1481522,"uid":170601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:47:18.000Z","msg":"元朗可疑私家車掉出一箱汽油彈 警拘中港3男<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1CwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=175f3412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】警方在元朗撞破藏汽油彈案，今日(15日)凌晨1時許，警員在青山公路屏山段往天水圍方向巡邏時，發現一輛形迹可疑私家車停泊上址，遂上前截查，站在車旁的3名男子見狀，隨即拔足向元朗市方向逃走，被警員追捕擒獲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n私家車則由司機駕駛向屯門方向逃去，期間，車上掉出一個紙箱，警員檢查發現紙箱內有7個懷疑汽油彈，經初步調查後，以涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途，將擒獲的3名男子拘捕，被捕3人中，其中2人姓李(26及35歲)，均為內地人，另1人姓程(61歲)，為本地人，當中35歲內地男子逃走時意外受傷，由救護員送院治療。案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝在逃司機及私家車，並追查藏汽油彈動機。"},{"pid":"c19ab7dd31421373e982a49989a9681de4bb41f0","tid":1481522,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"前線手足現家每一步都要好小心.<br />\n<br />\n我方在明, 敵方在暗"},{"pid":"b4329e0c2a09adc5d1106d11a1b80ca01692062d","tid":1481522,"uid":36089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:56:48.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借一借位～<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國散戶已經唔比隨便攞美金<br />\n各手足要襯香港可以自由兌換既時間行動<br />\n6個月前既你有無諗到香港今日係咁?</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保護自己資產，全民唱美元現鈔！</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478882\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478882</a>"},{"pid":"8c294f5c3770e1378e611ef284b50ba34fe47e09","tid":1481522,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"【突發】英國紀錄片導演想搵人傾下香港人嘅故事，下年喺美國PBS同英國Channel 4廣播！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}